<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">为深入学习领会党的二十届三中全会精神，引导全体党员同志把思想和行动统一到党的二十届三中全会精神上来，经济管理学院学生党支部于9月24日在A10-314党员活动室召开了“学思践悟 深学笃行”主题党日活动。本次活动由学生党支部书记熊奕俊主持，学生支部全体党员参加。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240928/1727527867795008192.png" title="1727527867795008192.png" alt="d23c44eefac4a422561761024476ad9.png" width="821" height="643" style="width: 821px; height: 643px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240928/1727527886771020030.png" title="1727527886771020030.png" alt="1ca73114338a01f4aca87ee9c0d08f8.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240928/1727527915680048243.png" title="1727527915680048243.png" alt="756ef584ce4f3d13fd3d571d8a92608.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240928/1727527931378059565.png" title="1727527931378059565.png" alt="963c15550ab20bc1e368c9396e51797.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240928/1727528058043025911.png" title="1727528058043025911.png" alt="bccd0cc34691dda0a5089e957d5f330.png" width="838" height="790" style="width: 838px; height: 790px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240928/1727528090476089289.png" title="1727528090476089289.png" alt="e74c94302fee7f89f65cf23ba95241f.png" width="836" height="880" style="width: 836px; height: 880px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240928/1727528183092089997.png" title="1727528183092089997.png" alt="4be763fc0d5766915d3f9e4afc0c01f.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;">学思践悟 ，深学笃行，通过此次主题党日活动，全体党员纷纷表示，在今后的工作中将以更加饱满的工作热情、更加良好的精神状态、更加昂扬的斗志和更加务实的工作作风，埋头实干，锐意进取，不懈奋斗！</p>